headline: Hillphoenix Recognized by EPA with GreenChill Store Certification Excellence Award for 13th Consecutive Year
summary: Hillphoenix, part of Dover Food Retail and Dover (NYSE: DOV) and a pioneer in designing environmentally sustainable refrigeration systems, has earned the U.S. Environmental Protection Agency's (EPA's) GreenChill 2023-2024 Store Certification Excellence recognition.
